      "rationale": "At MRL 5 for a Class III device, software quality assurance requires documented version control, regression testing, and independent code review. The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R2) is used under a validated installation with documented QA procedures including regression test suite passage and configuration management records.",
