      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "Numerical code verification at MRL 5 requires demonstration that the implemented numerical algorithms correctly solve the governing equations. Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) was applied to the Navier-Stokes and power-law hemolysis transport equations, confirming expected spatial convergence rates (2nd-order for velocity, 1st-order for hemolysis scalar).",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
