        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Code verification acceptance criteria",
        "description": "MMS verification must demonstrate convergence rates within 10% of theoretical order for all primary solution variables. Achieved: velocity fields converge at 1.94 order (theory: 2.0); hemolysis scalar at 0.97 order (theory: 1.0). Both within tolerance."
