        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Discretization error acceptance criteria",
        "description": "GCI on the fine mesh must be below 5% for all primary quantities of interest (NIH and pump head). Three-mesh GCI study required with refinement ratio ≥ 1.3. Achieved GCI values: NIH 4.2%, pump head 2.8% — both within threshold."
      }
    },
    {
