      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions for the FDA benchmark study are well-documented with calibrated instrumentation, controlled hematocrit (40% ± 1%), controlled temperature (37 ± 0.5 °C), and traceable flow measurement (Coriolis meter, ±0.5% full scale). Operating points span the clinical VAD range and are fully specified in the validation dataset.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
