        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Test conditions acceptance criteria",
        "description": "Experimental conditions must be documented with calibration traceability for all measurement instruments, controlled blood analog properties within ±2% of target, and operating points covering the COU envelope. All criteria met per FDA benchmark study documentation."
